<div id="secondary" class="widget-area manytilesbottom" role="complementary">
	<aside id="text-3" class="widget widget_text"><h1 class="widget-title">About me</h1>			<div class="textwidget"><img src="http://dcm-ki.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/avatar.png" />
<p class="aboutme">At 70, I have attended quite a few funerals. But sometimes it's hard to celebrate the life of friends or family members because I feel that some funerals don't suit the personality of the deceased. My ability to remember details of ceremonies which worked well means that other family and friends often ask for my help if they have to organise a service. I am constantly keeping an eye out for new ideas and funeral homes which focus on capturing the deceased's individuality. I thought I would share the most interesting suggestions I come across in this blog for anyone else who might need to help with a funeral. Thank you for browsing.
</p></div>
